LastLog - show listing of last logged in players

COMMANDS, PERMISSION, COMMENT
/firstlog [pagenumber] - lastlog.firstlog - list the most recent first logins of players
/lastlog [pagenumber] - lastlog.lastlog - list the most recent last logins of players
/loginfo [playername] - lastlog.loginfo - display first and last login date of a player

OTHER PERMISSIONS
lastlog.notify - receive notification when a player joins for the first time

INSTALLATION
Copy the LastLog.jar into the plugins folder. Restart Bukkit.

CONFIGURATION
Except for permissions, none.
